aring. The peak flare luminosity in the 0.3-8 keV band is $\\approx12\\%$ of\nthe pulsar's spin-down power, which may require magnetic reconnection. None of\nthese three systems has yet shown a transition back to an accreting state.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Sep 2018 16:02:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-24"}
