 nuclear matters and that chiral magnetic effects\ndisappear in strong coupled QGP.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 2 Sep 2018 01:44:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Mar 2019 02:22:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-20"}
