hows the presence of the phantom fluid and leads towards\nthe expansion of the universe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 2 Sep 2018 14:11:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Oct 2018 08:51:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-20"}
